-   `C_{i+1}` is constructed from `C_i`. If `C_i` is non-empty, `C_{i+1}` is `C_i` plus the formula `δ` (which is the `i`-th formula in some enumeration) such that `P(δ) → ξ ∉ T` and `C_i` implies `δ`.
